channel.title: Sound Extracting
channel.description: Since the cache extractor isn't working, I tried using someone's Midi Dumper. It gave me plenty of .mid files but they were unreadable. So I thought maybe the sounds are stored in a diffrent .idx file. So I tried every .idx file and none of them gave me readable sound files. An I doing something wrong?
